<span id="Cameras_and_objects_tools"></span>
=== Outils des caméras et des objets ===

* [[Image:Movie_CreateMovieCamera.svg|24px]] [[Movie_CreateMovieCamera/fr|MovieCamera]]

* [[Image:Movie_EnableMovieCamera.svg|24px]] [[Movie_EnableMovieCamera/fr|Enable a MovieCamera]]

* [[Image:Movie_SetMoviePosA.svg|24px]] [[Movie_SetMoviePosA/fr|Set position A]]

* [[Image:Movie_SetMoviePosB.svg|24px]] [[Movie_SetMoviePosB/fr|Set position B]]

* [[Image:Movie_CreateMovieObjects.svg|24px]] [[Movie_CreateMovieObjects/fr|MovieObjects]]

* [[Image:Movie_EnableMovieObjects.svg|24px]] [[Movie_EnableMovieObjects/fr|Enable a MovieObjects]]

* [[Image:Movie_SetMovieObjectsAxis.svg|24px]] [[Movie_SetMovieObjectsAxis/fr|Set an axis]]

* [[Image:Movie_ExcludeMovieObjects.svg|24px]] [[Movie_ExcludeMovieObjects/fr|Exclude a MovieObjects]]

